{"title":"历史的记忆不会褪色——贺香港回归祖国","authors":["白朝蓉"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的记忆不会褪色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——贺香港回归祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白朝蓉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史并不遥远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百余年外侮的沉重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压弯了中国人的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也惊醒了中国人的国殇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙中山用粤语昭告天下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要废除不平等条约”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要收回租借的土地”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党政府力不从心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既无严辞以对谬论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更无实力以抗凶顽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有理者因有理而失败"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无理者因无理而制胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港回归的曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由一位世纪伟人点燃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平一语千钧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主权不能谈判！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港必须如期回归！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两年多的唇枪舌剑之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百多年的不平等啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于被邓小平一举摆平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他，亦将在大海中永生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住１９９７年７月１日吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"米字旗从皇后大道滑落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗从维多利亚升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫荆花旗插遍香港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殖民主义在东方寿终正寝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是多么激动人心的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是多么光耀青史的篇章！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：内蒙古广播电视厅）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}